metatags.twitter:title: Georgia Digital Driver’s License and ID in Google Wallet Now Available for Android Users
metatags.og:title: Georgia Digital Driver’s License and ID in Google Wallet Now Available for Android Users
metatags.og:description: Commissioner Spencer R. Moore, Georgia Department of Driver Services (DDS), is pleased to announce the launch of the Agency’s latest milestone: Georgia Digital Driver’s License and ID in Google Wallet. Once added, customers can securely present their digital driver’s license or ID using Android smartphones at select Transportation Security Administration (TSA) PreCheck® security checkpoints, including those within Hartsfield-Jackson Atlanta International Airport.

metatags.twitter:title: Georgia Expands Digital Driver's License and ID Program to Include Samsung Wallet
metatags.og:title: Georgia Expands Digital Driver's License and ID Program to Include Samsung Wallet
metatags.og:description: The Georgia Department of Driver Services (DDS) is excited to announce the expansion of its Digital Driver's License and ID Program to include Samsung Wallet. This enhancement provides Georgia residents who have a Samsung Galaxy with a secure, convenient, and innovative way to manage their identification documents.

metatags.twitter:title: Georgia Digital Driver’s License and ID for Holiday Air Travel
metatags.og:title: Georgia Digital Driver’s License and ID for Holiday Air Travel
metatags.og:description: If your holiday vacation plans involve flying, remember to add your Georgia Digital Driver's License or State ID to your Apple Wallet or Google Wallet!  While it is not a replacement for your physical copy, your Georgia Digital Driver’s License or ID can speed up the process at select Transportation Safety Administration (TSA) PreCheck® checkpoints including Atlanta Hartsfield Jackson International Airport’s South Terminal.
